-- Russia Bans Ukrainian Tankers Made by Azovmash, Kommersant Says
-- B y   K a t e r y n a   C h o u r s i n a
-- 2012-04-06T07:16:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-06/russia-bans-ukrainian-tankers-made-by-azovmash-kommersant-says.html
Russia’s federal agency for railway
transport banned the use of tankers produced by Ukraine’s
Azovmash OJSC,  Kommersant-Ukraine  newspaper reported, citing an
official in the agency.  To contact the reporter on this story:
